Your Oct. 2 page one topic on top people wey dey ride so-so called "railbikes" on top of railway track, na disservice for una readers.

It actually encourages oder people to do very dangerous, and illegal activity wey only few people dey do now.

E dey do all dis tins for majik; majik wey dey kause wahala and e dey kause wahala for pipol.

Saul Resnick

